= SDL_version =
A structure that contains information about the version of SDL in use.


== Data Fields ==
{|
|Uint8 
|'''major''' 
|major version 
|-
|Uint8 
|'''minor''' 
|minor version 
|-
|Uint8 
|'''patch''' 
|update version (patchlevel)
|}

